unittitle_ssm: Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Collection of Asia Serials
abstract_ssm: The Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Collection of Asia Serials contains over 100 titles published in and about East Asia and Southeast Asia between 1940 and 2008.  The bulk of the collection dates from the 1970s and the 1980s.  Topics include political and social issues throughout Asia, arts in Asia, and Asian American communities and organizations in the United States.
